{"tid":2284050,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方對兩宗針對警務人員的嚴重違法事件予以嚴厲譴責","createTime":"2020-11-13T04:19:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-13T13:32:41.000Z","uid":3302,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"18fabd201f70e799f91417a836c925d7a04bb625","tid":2284050,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"警方表示，昨日發生兩宗針對警務人員的嚴重違法事件。<br />\n<br />\n警方在社交網站表示，昨日下午3時許，有人懷疑在葵涌邨停車場，刻意破壞警務人員車輛並逃去；在晚上9時許，有人虛報在東涌富東邨有打鬥案件發生，警員在現場調查期間，有人從高處向警員投擲懷疑裝有腐蝕性液體的容器，該容器在地面爆開、液體四濺，情況極度危險。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，有關事件肆意挑戰法律，更嚴重危害公眾安全，予以嚴厲譴責，必定全力追緝涉案人士，將其繩之於法。"},{"pid":"33f36568b10e4afe80f170fd0378a1ab33494150","tid":2284050,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:20:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559744-20201113.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559744-20201113.htm&d=28xXuG3%2BZgR4L17YEenOIgmnwACYIcySctyK7icvN2A%3D&h=66a59fb0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1559744-20201113.htm&h=ec7410bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1559744-20201113.htm</a>"},{"pid":"087cd5827ee2967186a3b239e429f625e5e9f08f","tid":2284050,"uid":335401,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:21:36.000Z","msg":"捉唔到人然後事但捉幾個唔順超嘅返狗屋玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d62e65b28b0ba07fb276c6670d3d822c224289ac","tid":2284050,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"黑吃黑，又想老屈？"},{"pid":"eba86d32c4e1efba5b857dd772ae4805e514a6fa","tid":2284050,"uid":352936,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-13T04:22:57.000Z","msg":"少少野就話危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/no